  "detailed_description": "Easy to play, very hard to finish. Can you beat <strong>The World's Hardest Game 3D 2</strong>?<br><br><strong>The World's Hardest Game</strong>, which you used to play on flash game sites, is now with you in 3D. Good luck in this challenging game of 30 unique levels!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cute graphics and colorful atmosphere<br></li><li>Smooth gameplay<br></li><li>30 Different challenging main levels and 8 unique levels !<br></li><li>Nice and different soundtracks<br></li><li>Long Play Time <br></li><li>New levels will be added with updates<br></li><li>Auto save system</li></ul><br><strong>You can customize your Cube with different trails and colors !</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Top Down View</h2>You can change to <strong>Top Down View</strong> to see the whole level, but you can't move in <strong>Top Down View</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815450/extras/9c421a8ee9b3c0157ac51a4b60ff4f6e.avif?t=1659283386\" width=184 height=212 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815450/extras/6819e4ce1185a3bc249769834cb1ba86.avif?t=1659283386\" width=286 height=160 /></span>",
